{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/extras/ThousandsOfLeaves.gif?t=1739373504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are thousands of leaves in the yard, and your job is to keep it clean. Rake and blow leaves into compost bins, upgrading your tools to keep up with the ever-increasing waves of leaves in this satisfying yard cleaning simulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/extras/UpgradeRakeUntilItsSuperAwesom.gif?t=1739373504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your tools to collect more leaves at a time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/extras/AddCompostBin.gif?t=1739373504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy compost bins to keep up with the leaves as they creep over larger portions of the yard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/extras/NewRound.gif?t=1739373504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect all the leaves to advance to the next round!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the rake to drag leaves around</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the leaf blower to move large amounts of leaves away from a pivot point</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade the rake and leaf blower to move larger amounts of leaves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect leaves in compost bins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Add more compost bins to keep up with leaves as they spawn in a larger area</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade the compost bins to increase leaf capacity</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 additional leaf skins that can increase the points per round</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect hundreds of thousands of leaves across three hand-designed environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clear each wave of leaves to progress through this satisfying yard-cleaning simulator</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739373504","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/page.bg.jpg?t=1739373504","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/52af3935564b8472ae1b7838a9bd066c678d08a2/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739373504","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/52af3935564b8472ae1b7838a9bd066c678d08a2/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739373504","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/extras/ThousandsOfLeaves.gif?t=1739373504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are thousands of leaves in the yard, and your job is to keep it clean. Rake and blow leaves into compost bins, upgrading your tools to keep up with the ever-increasing waves of leaves in this satisfying yard cleaning simulation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487850/extras/UpgradeRakeUntilItsSuperAwesom.gif?t=1739373504\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your tools to collect more leaves at a time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_it